Description_lang: Your critical strikes have a chance to build Static Electricity, granting $s2% attack speed per stack. This effect may occur every $proccooldown sec.At $s3 stacks lightning surges through you, increasing your movement speed by $s4% for $s1 seconds. While surging, your auto attacks jolt your target and 1 nearby enemy for $s5 Nature damage.When this effect fades, you become grounded for $397621d and unable to generate Static Electricity.
